  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your task:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔍  Observe the rooms through the cameras.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚡Fix anomalies before they get out of hand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⏳ Last the whole night: from 00:00 to 06:00.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345760/extras/4450ff1ed2ba004762a0082f23e2afad.poster.avif?t=1772391198\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345760/extras/4450ff1ed2ba004762a0082f23e2afad.webm?t=1772391198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345760/extras/4450ff1ed2ba004762a0082f23e2afad.mp4?t=1772391198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features of the game:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💀 540 unique anomalies are waiting for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔒 23 secret endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👁️ Every change is a challenge to your attention and endurance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏚️ Deep atmosphere of fear and tension.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📹 Unique mechanics: observe, analyze, act.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎯 Only the most attentive will be able to reveal all the secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345760/extras/39d2f6065cfb33d41b8be5308faceb8d.poster.avif?t=1772391198\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345760/extras/39d2f6065cfb33d41b8be5308faceb8d.webm?t=1772391198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345760/extras/39d2f6065cfb33d41b8be5308faceb8d.mp4?t=1772391198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Secret Endings:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some anomalies have multiple stages and will change if not dealt with immediately. They can move between rooms. If you hear a heartbeat, it means you are in danger. Watch the cameras and see the anomaly in its entirety, but act in time to avoid danger!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345760/extras/7ee471009e2548b993700dc0f0b07e68.poster.avif?t=1772391198\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345760/extras/7ee471009e2548b993700dc0f0b07e68.webm?t=1772391198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345760/extras/7ee471009e2548b993700dc0f0b07e68.mp4?t=1772391198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
